                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-2" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The instructors of the TOGAF Course by KnowledgeHut are industry experts and trainers who themselves have TOGAF Certifications and are a part of professionals with hands-on experience. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-3">3. How are the workshops structured?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Our TOGAF course focuses on engaging interaction. Most class time is dedicated to fun exercises, lively discussions, and team collaboration - all facilitated by the trainer. The focus is on practical solutions to real-world challenges drawn from decades of experience as Agile coaches, and leaders in Kanban environments. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-4">4. Are course materials and workshop instructions provided in advance? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-4" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, your course material will be provided in advance. You will receive an email with a link to set your password a few days in advance of the scheduled course. You will have access to the study plan and all the course material. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-5">5. What course material will I receive?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-5" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The course material comprises of the course schedule or study plan, workbooks and all relevant assignments, assessments, or case studies. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-6">6. Can I record the session? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-6" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The sessions would be auto recorded on our LMS, subject to permission by The Open Group and the instructor. Based on the permissions, you would have lifetime access to the video recordings of the sessions as well.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-7">7. Can I use my phone or tab for the training?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-7" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>No, you will not yet be able to join the training through phone or tab. Please be prepared to join the training on your laptop or desktop. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-8">8. What if I lose internet connection during the training? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-8" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>If you get disconnected during the training, you will have the option to re-join within about half an hour subject to accreditation body guidelines and the instructor’s preference. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-9">9. Where will the TOGAF workshop be held? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-9" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Our workshops are currently held online. Anyone with a stable internet connectivity, from any desired place across the world, can benefit from the workshop and get certified as a Professional Agile Leader. You can check out the schedules <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">here</a>: &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-10">10. How do I join the class?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-10" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>You will receive a registration link from us to your e-mail id. You can set your password, log in and start your immersive learning journey. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-11">11. What if I miss a class?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-11" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>If you miss a class, you can access the recordings of the sessions, provided Scrum.org and the instructor have permitted recordings. At the beginning of every session, there will also be a 10-12-minute recapitulation of the previous class. &nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-12">12. Is this a live training, or will I watch pre-recorded videos? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-12" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>You will get the benefit of both since this is a blended learning workshop.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-13">13. What platform do you use for video conferencing?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-13" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>We currently use the Zoom platform for video conferencing and will soon be adding more integrations with WebEx and Microsoft Teams. However, all the sessions and the recordings will be available right from within our learning platform. Learners will not need to wait for any notifications or links or install any additional software.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-14">14. Will I have other participants in the class?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-14" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, there will be other participants who will actively participate in the class remotely. They can attend online training from office, home, or any other suitable place. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-15">15. How does the 24/7 support work?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-15" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>In case of any queries, our support team is available to you 24/7 via the Help and Support section. You can also reach out to your workshop manager on your workshop group messenger. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-16">16. I have some more doubts. How can I get them cleared? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-16" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Should you have any more questions, please email us on <a href="http://support@oneitech.com" target="_blank">support@oneitech.com</a> and we will be happy to get back to you. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="finance-related-faqs-4">
                            <h3>Finance-Related FAQs</h3>
                            <div class="course-cert-faq-content accordion-cards custom-cards" id="faq-accordion-4">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-1">1. Can I cancel my enrolment to the TOGAF course? Do I get a refund?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-1" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>You can cancel your enrolment and receive refunds in line with our Cancellations and Refunds policy found at <a href="#" target="_blank">#</a>. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-2">2. Is the certification fee inclusive of the TOGAF course fee?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-2" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, the TOGAF certification fee is included in KnowledgeHut’s training fee. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-3">3. Can I switch my start date?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, you may switch your start date with prior notice of at least 24 hrs. and subject to availability in the desired batch. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-4">4. Is there a money-back guarantee?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-4" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, we have a 100% money-back guarantee in line with our <a href="#" target="_blank">100% Satisfaction Guarantee policy</a>. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-5">5. Are there any scholarships available? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-5" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, scholarships are available for students and veterans with grants that can vary up to 50% of the course fees. &nbsp;</p>
                                            <p>To avail scholarships, please get in touch with us at <a href="http://support@oneitech.com" target="_blank">support@oneitech.com</a>. The team shall send across the forms and instructions to you. Based upon the responses and answers that we receive, our panel of experts take a decision on the Grant. The entire process could take about 7 to 15 days. </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-6">6. Are there any group discounts? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-6" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, group discounts are available and apply to groups as small as three (3) participants. The more participants that attend a training course, the greater the discount. By registering in groups, you can typically save up 20% to 30% on the course fee. For more details, please check out <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">upcoming schedules</a>. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-7">7. Can I pay the course fees in instalments? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-7" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, instalment options are available for payment of course fees. To avail the instalment option, please get in touch with us at <a href="http://support@oneitech.com" target="_blank">support@oneitech.com</a>. The team will explain how the instalments work and provide timelines for your case. Typically, the number of instalments varies from 2 to 3, but the full amount must be paid before you complete the course. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
